Package: heavytailcombtest
Type: Package
Title: Aggregating Dependent Signals with Heavy-Tailed Combination Tests
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Lin", "Gui", email = "glin6@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides (weighted) heavy-tailed combination test for global testing. Heavy-tailed        
    distributions include Cauchy, Log Cauchy, Levy, Pareto, Frechet, t, and Inverse Gamma.
